- But before that a joint with Babaji.

- Food , whisky(RS) and Music on the mountain peaks with the Himachal locals

- Another joint on the way back.

- Bakes and Brews - for a chicken burger , Cream rolls and pastry .

- The day ended with a home theatre animated movie - STORKS .

What a Day ! 9/10